  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >is a hard core 'AI' based MUD.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3343330/extras/9c4f16138d30c92a35862146553a3df6.avif?t=1736469628\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3343330/extras_big/9c4f16138d30c92a35862146553a3df6.avif?t=1736469628 width=800 height=400 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Just leave it running and the game progress will continue to advance.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3343330/extras/decfae7ed9ce6c50355810e7e44885c0.avif?t=1736469628\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3343330/extras_big/decfae7ed9ce6c50355810e7e44885c0.avif?t=1736469628 width=800 height=400 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Heros have great skills and talents.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3343330/extras/83dfa872b13ca6ba8d65ac7c5b4ab357.avif?t=1736469628\" width=602 height=620 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >With the 'AI' written by the player themselves, the heros can 'smartly' handle various emergencies。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3343330/extras/9493ca0bb3859bc668c140433556c381.avif?t=1736469628\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3343330/extras_big/9493ca0bb3859bc668c140433556c381.avif?t=1736469628 width=800 height=400 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >is a hard core 'AI' based MUD.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3343330/extras/9c4f16138d30c92a35862146553a3df6.avif?t=1736469628\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3343330/extras_big/9c4f16138d30c92a35862146553a3df6.avif?t=1736469628 width=800 height=400 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Just leave it running and the game progress will continue to advance.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3343330/extras/decfae7ed9ce6c50355810e7e44885c0.avif?t=1736469628\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3343330/extras_big/decfae7ed9ce6c50355810e7e44885c0.avif?t=1736469628 width=800 height=400 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Heros have great skills and talents.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3343330/extras/83dfa872b13ca6ba8d65ac7c5b4ab357.avif?t=1736469628\" width=602 height=620 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >With the 'AI' written by the player themselves, the heros can 'smartly' handle various emergencies。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3343330/extras/9493ca0bb3859bc668c140433556c381.avif?t=1736469628\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3343330/extras_big/9493ca0bb3859bc668c140433556c381.avif?t=1736469628 width=800 height=400 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
